704341f-a.title: Brooklyn: Flatbush Avenue - Willoughby Street
704341f-a.text:
Flatbush Avenue Extension, at the S. W. corner of
Willoughby Str et, showing Green's used-car sales denot.
The trolley tracks are on Willoughby Street, running across
Slatbush Avenue Extension.
April 17, 1940
L. Sperr

704335f-a.text:
Flatbush Avenue Extension, north frow Prince Street
